Blair scored 144 points
this football season.

00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:09.084
He scored all his points
with 50-yard field goal--

00:00:09.084 --> 00:00:10.500
that's actually
pretty impressive.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:11.000
50.

